sources.title: Independents' Day | Full Movie | Action Adventure | Happy 4th Of July!
sources.description:
Independents' Day - Aliens invade, this time delivering a clear ultimatum. The fate of humanity hangs in the balance as the U.S. President and citizens decide if these aliens are to be trusted ...or feared.
2016. Stars: Fay Gauthier, Sal Landi, Johnny Rey Diaz
